  ## Get Hotel Count - Master Database
  
  ### Endpoint:
  GET /api/v1/hotels/sync/master-data/count
  
  ### Service Method Called:
  `getHotelCount()` - Returns count of hotels in tbo_hotel_master table
  
  ### Response Example:
  {
    "hotelCount": 96,
    "message": "Total hotels in master database: 96"
  }
  
  ### Purpose:
  Check how many hotels have been synced to the database
  before and after running full sync.
}
